				<p>Athenian eAcademy is committed to providing a working and learning environment free from harassment, prohibited discrimination and retaliation. The charter values diversity among its students and employees. Accordingly, no otherwise qualified person shall be excluded from participation in, be denied the benefits of, or otherwise be subjected to unlawful discrimination in any charter program or activity on the basis of age, color, disability, gender, gender identity, genetic information, national origin, pregnancy, race, religion, sexual orientation, or veteran status.</p>
